{"tid":2085491,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國商務部長羅斯宣布，撤銷對香港的特殊待遇地位","createTime":"2020-06-30T02:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T02:39:57.000Z","uid":136988,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"16847c4d4ac70f2444e93cebb1f285252a6a8bf0","tid":2085491,"uid":136988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:02:13.000Z","msg":"羅斯在聲明中表示，隨著北京政府對香港實施港區國安法，美國商務部決定暫停執行對香港提供相關優惠待遇的法規。羅斯呼籲中國政府立即作出改變，兌現對港人的承諾。<br />\n<br />\n較早前，美國國務卿蓬佩奧在聲明中表示，美方停止向香港出口軍用設備，形容是已經不能分清楚，向中國大陸抑或香港出口受管制物品，為避免這些設備落入解放軍手中，美方被迫採取行動，保障美國國家安全。<br />\n<br />\n即係咩?"},{"pid":"a5d055da37471f1d39e8a54946dbccecd3c93478","tid":2085491,"uid":156652,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:03:02.000Z","msg":"即係要返工"},{"pid":"92b954d57d53a189eefbac141a3a1648cf2553b7","tid":2085491,"uid":55669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:03:29.000Z","msg":"補返醬 <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534817-20200630.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534817-20200630.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=adb5b2db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534817-20200630.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4df3d4df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534817-20200630.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"9705815c281bbacb8fcac9a32776b0e0c93ea9f3","tid":2085491,"uid":22590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:04:16.000Z","msg":"代表恆指升"},{"pid":"3d0c1cd6a5abfdbe471a5e53863b489fec55f934","tid":2085491,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:04:42.000Z","msg":"本來有啲咩設備？"},{"pid":"2b3e45800987854f4a876e50827c013a13372cc1","tid":2085491,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2